OL,3,CMan died hours after being escorted
OL,4,Coff a plane in Turkey
OL,6,FA man died in a fall after being
OL,7,Fescorted off a plane in Turkey for
OL,8,Fintoxicated behaviour, an inquest has
OL,9,Fheard.
OL,11,FBen Crook, from Caerphilly, was
OL,12,Fremoved from the flight on landing in
OL,13,FAntayla in September 2024 and was
OL,14,Fseparated from partner and two
OL,15,Fchildren.
OL,17,FMr Crook was said to have been
OL,18,Fbehaving erratically and shouting at
OL,19,Fthe flight attendants before smashing
OL,20,Fboth his and his partner's phones,
OL,21,FGwent Coroner's Court heard.
