OL,3,CMan died hours after being escorted
OL,4,Coff a plane in Turkey
OL,6,FHe had also brought alcohol from duty
OL,7,Ffree to drink on arrival.
OL,9,FDuring the flight, evidence from his
OL,10,Fpartner Jess Jenkins said Mr Crook's
OL,11,Fbehaviour changed and he began
OL,12,Fshouting at a male steward, demanding
OL,13,Falcohol.
OL,15,FHe then broke both his and Ms Jenkins'
OL,16,Fmobile phones and as a result was
OL,17,Fescorted off the plane.
