OL,3,CMan died hours after being escorted
OL,4,Coff a plane in Turkey
OL,6,FThe inquest heard Mr Crook never
OL,7,Freached his hotel later, but had tried
OL,8,Fto contact his father and partner
OL,9,Fafter borrowing a phone from a couple
OL,10,Fhe had met.
OL,12,FThe couple said Mr Crook looked
OL,13,F"shaken and hungover" and they had
OL,14,Flast seen him walking across the
OL,15,Fharbour.
OL,17,FHis family had reported him missing
OL,18,Fafter he had not arrived at the hotel.
