OL,3,CMan died hours after being escorted
OL,4,Coff a plane in Turkey
OL,6,FEvidence from Mr Crook's sister Amy
OL,7,Fsaid her brother had had issues with
OL,8,Fdrugs and alcohol and his consumption
OL,9,Fhad increased in the months before his
OL,10,Fdeath.
OL,12,FBut she added that there was nothing
OL,13,Fto suggest he would take his own life
OL,14,Fand leave his two children without a
OL,15,Ffather.
OL,17,FA toxicology report revealed the
OL,18,Fpresence of cocaine, alcohol, ketamine
OL,19,Fand cocaethylene in Mr Crook's blood,
OL,20,Fwith the ketamine likely given to him
OL,21,Fduring his treatment.
