OL,4,Coff a plane in Turkey
OL,6,FDelivering her conclusion, Ms Saunders
OL,7,Fsaid: "(Alcohol and drugs) may have
OL,8,Fcaused disorientation and poor
OL,9,Fjudgement but this is insufficient to
OL,10,Fdetermine he fell as a result of the
OL,11,Fdrugs he had taken.
OL,13,F"I find the fall was an accident, the
OL,14,Fexact details of which are unknown..."
OL,16,FThe coroner offered her sincere
OL,17,Fcondolences to Mr Crook's family in
OL,18,Fthe courtroom.
